        "heading": "Nationally, early-dose coverage is high but completion still drops",
        "body": "The national sequence shows a clear taper from first to later doses. In 2025, OPV 1 is 93.0 and OPV 2 is 89.5, then OPV 3 drops to 83.0. A similar pattern appears for IPV, with IPV 1 at 89.1 and IPV 2 at 78.9. Polio 3 at 83.3 confirms that completion is lower than first-dose contact."
      },
      {
        "heading": "Regional divide is wide for later-dose outcomes",
